title: Home
text: Economic Analytics is a consultancy founded in 2022 by Christian Spence. We work with a variety of clients from not-for-profits, trade bodies, local authorities through to blue-chip companies to provide economic and economic data-led research to support research and analysis, decision making, modelling and forecasting.
